Quiet places & Soft moments 🤍

I use to think I had to do certain things and hit certain goals before turning 30. But age is just a number, it doesn’t define who we are, what we achieved or what we CAN still accomplish. 

I look back at what I have accomplished and I can’t be more proud of myself. I am exactly where I need to be and I’m grateful and blessed for all that I have and all that I am. 

I’m grateful for my parents, my brother, my family and friends. I wouldn’t be where I am today if it wasn’t for all your love & support. 

I’m grateful for all the lessons, mistakes, and heartaches. I’m grateful for all the love, happiness, and successes that I accomplished. 

Bye-bye twenties 🖤
Cheers to 30, flirty, & thriving 🎂♥️
